section: == Biography == | === Backing band and 1986 Omega Tribe ===

sentences: From 1979 to 1985, Kurokawa was a part of the backing bands of Hiromi Iwasaki and Momoko Kikuchi as a part of the Pineapple Company.
section: == Biography == | === Backing band and 1986 Omega Tribe ===

sentences: In 1986, he left the backing bands and joined the band 1986 Omega Tribe as a second guitarist and band leader.
section: == Biography == | === Backing band and 1986 Omega Tribe ===

sentences: Kurokawa stopped playing music due to his condition, but resumed his activities in 2007 as a solo artist, and was active in various fields and supported Brand New Omega Tribe's vocalist Arai Masahito and the band KEICO.
section: == Biography == | === Backing band and 1986 Omega Tribe ===

sentences: On June 6, 2020, Kurokawa died from sepsis.
